Hi Scott,
Those and the later types are reusable.

  Does the cupped side with the metal  > spring face towards the inner 
> bearing/race or towards the spindle?

Bearing/race.

>>  Also, should that seal sit flush with he drum?<<

Should, but we have had some just barely stick out.  Measure the bore for the 
seal to see if it should be recessed.
